  <Heading title="The Process" subtitle="" />

  <Heading3
    title="1. Structuring Complex Data (UX)"
    subtitle="Before writing any code, I had to untangle the relational data. I designed dashboard layouts that prioritized critical daily tasks—allowing hostel staff to instantly cross-reference available products, track vendor stock, and manage meal allocations based on guest diet types. The goal was to reduce cognitive load and minimize clicks for high-frequency actions."
  />

